description: The Mayan God of the Underworld, Bolon Yokte K’u, is at his strongest when the star Sagittarius A is aligned with the center of our galaxy (also known as the Dark Rift). This happens every 5,000 years, and this alignment is happening right now. Aided by a giant, mythological puma made of stone, K'u intends to network the Valley of the Volcanoes (in Peru) with the molten rivers of Xibilba (Mayan Hell), and activate them all at once. This will ruin the atmosphere of the planet, causing plants, animals and even humans to expire. K’u also attempted such a plan some five thousand years ago, but a Mesoamerican Creation God, Viracocha, stopped him. After being contacted by William Aether (the ESOU medium) Viracocha has offered to help try to stop K'u again. However, Viracocha now lacks followers and is a mere shadow of the God he once was when he thwarted K'u eons ago. Unruffled, K'u prepares to unleash the final cog in the wheel that will turn his vision into reality, a new beginning...for a DARK WORLD.
name: Transmission of Will

description:
Home

The shocking conclusion to Volume One. As Anya finally engages Ngeve, she learns a devastating truth that casts new light on what she thought of both her family and her enemies. No one is safe as Ngeve's forces step up their efforts to protect the program, bringing this chapter to an unexpected - and tragic - finale.
name: Home

description:
Wahey! Dennis the Menace and Gnasher celebrate Pancake Day by tossing pancakes Menace-style! Watch out, Walter! Harr-harr!

Also in Beanotown this week...

  • Zombie footballer, Chewie Suarez plays his heart out!
  • The Bash Street Squelchies know how to celebrate Valentine's Day... or do they?
  • How will Roger dodge a sloppy kiss from his aunt?

PLUS... learn how to make a paperclip slingshot, win TMNT prizes and all your favourite comic strips!

Enter The Dragon King

All worlds collide in an epic high-flying, sword slicing Game Of Death. Jack and Billy Blaze face-off with the ruthless gangster and Martial Arts extraordinaire, Master Ryujin. Meanwhile, Cicada is forced to face her demons and realize the terrorizing truth of her past life.
name: Enter The Dragon King

description:
Introduced by your host, The Bloke, a Victorian undertaker, who I dress as at conventions to promote the magazine. Bloke's Terrible Tomb of Terror is a homage to the classic horror anthology magazines that we grew up loving.

This is an ongoing, self-published series, with eleven issues currently available and two collected editions. Voted Best Anthology Of 2013 in the Ghastly Awards.

Sam gets a brief history lesson on The House, while Alex learns he has a new, game-changing talent. Also, Arthur discovers a source of immense power during a monster fight. Now, if he can only figure out a way to make people understand his plan...
Decoda, Syd, and Archangel Gabriel journey to the center of Hell to rescue Devah, who has been kidnapped by Siah.

Serialized from the pages of Dungeon Quest Book Three by Joe Daly, we join Millenium Boy, Millenium Boy, Steve, Nerd Girl and Lash Penis mid-adventure. A series of beasts called Womraxes attack the group, ripping off clothes right and left.
The series concludes as the heroes from multiple Earths join forces to take down the Gaslight Vandal Savage. Will Gaslight Luthor finally redeem himself?
name: Chapter Thirty-Six

volume.name: Infinite Crisis: Fight For the Multiverse

description:
CHIMA is under siege by the ancient ice hunter Tribe who are using their never-before seen powers to freeze anything they touch or blast at. The only way to fight these powerful opponents is to obtain and master the Fire CHI!

Note: The digital edition (2/11/2015) for this issue was released before the print edition.
name: The Power of Fire Chi

description:
The Tourist Trap

Swordi and Sorcera have hit the road, fleeing the temple of Moloch. What strange mysteries lie ahead in the hot springs of Mt. Frothmore?
name: The Tourist Trap

description:
The Unforgiving Sea

The North Shore of Oahu is moments from being reclaimed by the sea - a sea driving to wrath by the enormous projectile ejected from the summit at the highest point on Oahu. The race is on to reach the beach; for Maddy to find her grandfather.
name: The Unforgiving Sea

description: In the final chapter of the Neomad adventure, the Love Punks and Satellite Sisters must join forces to save a gigantic tourist shuttle from intergalactic catastrophe!
name: Book Three: Porkchop Plots

description: Mapped to Jospeh Campbell's Hero Cycle, Shon C. Bury's Nox is a self-aware low fantasy populated equally by mystical gurus, Everyman characters, and dark forces bent on tipping our mundane world into shadows. Nox is as influenced by Robert Graves' White Goddess and Jeremy Narby's Cosmic Serpent as Joseph Campell's The Hero With a Thousand Faces. Come join us on this epic road trip to end all epic road trips.

An Education

Homeschooling a super strong son and dealing with a brilliant daughter who's skipped grades isn't difficult enough for the Ramiro family. They are watching an ornery teenager for friends and Desert Fox has made someone angry enough that they plan to deal with her - permanently.
name: An Education

description: Washed-up Pro Wrestler, Mortie Q. Suggs, makes use of his newly attained superpowers. His first day as a Hero leads him to a bank heist and evil Axis of Doom. Also he crosses paths with the World's Greatest Champion: The Mighty American.

Includes a 3-month digital subscription! Weekly Shonen Jump is bridging the gap between print and digital! Get 100+ pages of manga including Naruto, Bleach, One Piece, Yu-Gi-Oh! Zexaland more! Includes a code for a 3-month weekly digital subscription, plus an Ultra Rare Weekly Shonen Jump exclusive Yu-Gi-Oh! promotional card and more!
name: Vol. 3

description: Tara Normal fights evil incarnate.
The day the Titans have been dreading all year has finally arrived. A day of unimaginable pain. Insurmountable loneliness. Inconceivable amounts of ice cream. That's right--it's Valentine's Day!
name: The Rocky Road To Love

description:
The Babysitter

In this world, redemption has a fixed price. What started as a simple job of babysitting the company's favorite bookkeeper ended with a lesson in redemption. In a city ruled by ruthless gangsters with dark secrets, two men hatch a plan to rob them blind and make their escape.
name: Book Three: The Babysitter

description: Private detective Velda's back on the stage shedding feathers as she finds herself up to her ears in counterfeiters when "Her Chips Come In"! Also in this issue, Velda learns what a didgeridoo does and in "Velda vs the DA" she gets a kick out of meeting her archenemy face to face! And as a special bonus, Velda's Special Paper Doll kit is included that features various clothing designs worn by Velda. An adventure of Neolithica: Girl of the Pleistocene and Hawkshaw Hawk: Bird Detective is also included.

The playback time on Ai's tape is winding down, and the only plan to make her human and save her from termination involves risking Yota's life! Ai, resigned to her fate and unwilling to put Yota's life on the line, wants to fade away quietly and give Yota a magic pill that will spare him the pain of remembering their doomed love...but the power of passion can't be overestimated! Everything comes together in the stunning climax of Video Girl Ai!
name: Fade Out

description: Bettina and her Booth Babe gang have a convention full of fans terrified as they commit an armed robbery. Outnumbered and unarmed, can Yaya use her powers to save the day?

There's a new Superstar in Slam City, and the WWE will never be the same! Enter the mysterious - El Diablo! But is he hero or villain? Friend or foe? And what role will he play in the Superstars'' ongoing battle with The Finisher? Find out all of this and more as several new Superstars make their first appearance in the Slam City graphic novels.

Note: The digital edition (2/11/2015) for this volume was released before the print edition.
